    "description": "Bavity, A fast paced puzzle game with balls and gravity.  Any group of 3 or more balls can be double clicked out of existence. Stop your screen from filling up, Its that simple.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nClassic mode,  Balls are spawned from a controllable hopper at regular intervals, Stop them reaching the top of the screen and blocking your hopper.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nPro Mode is Much more frantic, balls spawn anywhere along the top of the screen,  If there isn't anywhere to spawn the game is over.  <br />\r\n<br />\r\nSee your scores against other players and check your position on the leader boards.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nSave and continue playing at a later date,  Games are saved into the Steam cloud.",
